OL,3,CHeadteacher calls for more allergy
OL,4,Ceducation as hospital admissions triple
OL,6,FA Pontypridd headteacher is calling
OL,7,Ffor better allergy education and
OL,8,Ftraining for teachers across Wales.
OL,10,FIt comes as a new survey found that
OL,11,F95% of teachers had children with
OL,12,Fallergies in their schools, yet 67%
OL,13,Fhad no formal training.
OL,15,FJoanna Taylor knows the risks of an
OL,16,Fallergic reaction all too well. The St
OL,17,FMichael's Primary School headteacher
OL,18,Fsuffers from an allergy to fish and
OL,19,Fnuts.
