OL,3,CHeadteacher calls for more allergy
OL,4,Ceducation as hospital admissions triple
OL,6,FResearch by the NASUWT teachers' union
OL,7,Falong with The Natasha Allergy
OL,8,FResearch Foundation (NARF) found, 1 in
OL,9,F5 teachers have never been taught to
OL,10,Fuse an adrenaline auto-injector- an
OL,11,Fessential life saving tool in the
OL,12,Fevent of a severe allergic reaction.
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV Wales Ms Taylor said:
OL,15,F"Those stats actually made me feel sad
OL,16,Fand quite frustrated. I also suffer
OL,17,Fwith a nut and fish allergy and carry
OL,18,Fan auto-injector. So for me, I
OL,19,Funderstand how scary it is."
