OL,3,CHeadteacher calls for more allergy
OL,4,Ceducation as hospital admissions triple
OL,6,FAccording to the figures, 20% of all
OL,7,Ffood allergy reactions occur in
OL,8,Fschools, with hospital admissions for
OL,9,Ffood-induced anaphylaxis tripling in
OL,10,Fthe last 20 years. Despite this, the
OL,11,Fsurvey revealed that 60% of teachers
OL,12,Fdid not know if their school had an
OL,13,Fallergy policy.
OL,15,FMs Taylor has joined calls from the
OL,16,FNASUWT and NARF to introduce more
OL,17,Fresources and give adequate training
OL,18,Fto teachers.
