OL,3,CHeadteacher calls for more allergy
OL,4,Ceducation as hospital admissions triple
OL,6,FShe said: "One of the key messages is
OL,7,Fto follow the basic steps. Have those
OL,8,Faction plans in place and make sure
OL,9,Feveryone is aware (of the allergy),
OL,10,Fnot just the teacher that has that
OL,11,Fchild, but every single member of
OL,12,Fstaff in the school.
OL,14,F"Allergies can be fatal. So if we know
OL,15,Fwhere to go for specific training that
OL,16,Fwould make the difference for us to be
OL,17,Fable to help and have that link with
OL,18,Fparents so that they know their child
OL,19,Fis safe in the school environment they
OL,20,Fprovide."
