OL,3,CHeadteacher calls for more allergy
OL,4,Ceducation as hospital admissions triple
OL,6,FThe NASUWT has called on the
OL,7,Fgovernment to ensure schools receive
OL,8,Fthe necessary support and training to
OL,9,Fprotect children with food allergies.
OL,11,FIn a statement, the Welsh government
OL,12,Fsaid: "Our guidance says that staff
OL,13,Fshould be trained to recognise the
OL,14,Fsigns, symptoms and triggers of common
OL,15,Flife-threatening medical conditions
OL,16,Fand know what to do in an emergency.
