OL,6,F"All schools in Wales are also
OL,7,Fprovided with guidance on the use of
OL,8,Femergency adrenaline auto-injectors.
OL,9,FThe guidance is clear about the need
OL,10,Ffor staff to be trained to administer
OL,11,Finjectors."
